Package: runoutSIM
Title: Landslide Runout and Connectivity Simulation with Random Walks
Version: 1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Jason", "Goetz", , "jgoetz@wlu.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jia", "Huang", , "huan7147@mylaurier.ca", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Geospatial tools for simulating mass-movement runout using random 
  walk methods on digital elevation models (DEMs) and assessing connectivity to spatial features.
